**8. Payment Terms**

- Invoices are issued on the 25th of each month for the upcoming month of service.
- Payment is due by the 1st of the service month.
- Payments more than 7 days late may incur a 5% late fee.
- We reserve the right to suspend services for accounts more than 30 days in arrears.

By signing up for a service plan with The Astra Flow, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to the terms outlined in this Service Level Agreement.


